  "body": "Here (https://geth.ethereum.org/docs/interface/command-line-options) I can see that `--shh` flag exists, under `geth  v1.9.19-stable-3e064192`\r\n\r\n```\r\nWHISPER (EXPERIMENTAL) OPTIONS:\r\n  --shh                               Enable Whisper\r\n```\r\n\r\n-------\r\n\r\nBut on the `geth v1.10.1-stable-c2d2f4ed` ; `--shh` does not exist, is it completely removed?",
